terminal.help-text: Usage: Type a vocabulary after ">" (e. g. "amicus, amici m.", "laetus, laeta, laetum" or "felix, Gen. felicis"). Then after the indented ">", type the form you want to generate (e. g. "Nom. Sg." or "Gen. Pl. f."). To go back at any time, press enter without typing something on a prompt. Note: "Akk." is "Acc."!
